songs.title: Only Hungry For You
songs.lyrics:
Come give me love
You know I want it now
Come give me love
Oh baby, I will never let you get away
Come give me love and affection
All I want is a reaction from you
I’m only hungry for you

No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
No, no, no, I will never let you get away

Come give me love
You know I want it now
Come give me love
Oh, I will never let you get away
It’s true…

All I want is a reaction
All I need is a reaction from you
I’m only hungry for you

No, no, no, no!
No, no, no, I will never let you get away

No, I will never let you get away
Follow me until we stray
Oh, darling, yes
Is this a test?
I swear I will do my best
And I will pray everyday
So we can say we did it our way…

We did it our way…
We did it my way…

I will pray everyday
So we can say we did it our way…

We did it my way…
We did it our way…
